column1: query
SELECT MAX(Sales), COUNT(DISTINCT Theme) FROM journal
SELECT editor.Age, editor.Name FROM editor JOIN journal_committee ON editor.Editor_ID = journal_committee.Editor_ID GROUP BY editor.Name, editor.Age LIMIT 2
SELECT AVG(n.Age), n.Name FROM editor AS n WHERE Age IN (SELECT Age FROM editor WHERE Age <= 87 LIMIT 6) GROUP BY n.Name LIMIT 2;
SELECT Name FROM editor WHERE Age BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR Editor_ID IN (SELECT Editor_ID FROM editor AS a WHERE a.Editor_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  a.Age != 25)
SELECT Sales FROM journal WHERE  Sales != 32
SELECT AVG(Age), COUNT(DISTINCT Editor_ID), Age FROM editor WHERE (Editor_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR Editor_ID = 35) GROUP BY Age

SELECT b.Journal_ID, b.Editor_ID FROM journal_committee AS b WHERE b.Journal_ID > 96 AND b.Journal_ID NOT IN (SELECT z.Journal_ID FROM journal AS z WHERE z.Journal_ID <= 47 LIMIT 7) GROUP BY b.Journal_ID, b.Editor_ID HAVING MAX(b.Editor_ID) = 73 ORDER BY b.Editor_ID ASC
SELECT MIN(Sales), COUNT(DISTINCT Sales) FROM journal WHERE Journal_ID IN (SELECT Journal_ID FROM journal_committee WHERE Editor_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10)
SELECT Name FROM editor WHERE Editor_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 ORDER BY Name ASC LIMIT 7
SELECT Editor_ID, COUNT(Journal_ID) FROM journal_committee WHERE Journal_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY Editor_ID HAVING COUNT(Journal_ID) > 0 AND MIN(Editor_ID) < 86
SELECT AVG(Journal_ID), Journal_ID FROM journal_committee WHERE Journal_ID >= 86 OR Editor_ID = 60 ORDER BY Journal_ID ASC
SELECT editor.Name FROM editor WHERE editor.Editor_ID <= 35 GROUP BY editor.Name HAVING MIN(editor.Age) < 2 ORDER BY editor.Name DESC;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT e.Age), e.Editor_ID, e.Name FROM editor e GROUP BY e.Editor_ID, e.Name ORDER BY e.Name ASC;

SELECT editor.Age FROM journal_committee JOIN editor ON editor.Editor_ID = journal_committee.Editor_ID WHERE journal_committee.Editor_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND journal_committee.Work_Type NOT IN (SELECT Work_Type FROM journal_committee WHERE Journal_ID > 4 LIMIT 4) LIMIT 2
SELECT DISTINCT Work_Type FROM journal_committee WHERE Editor_ID >= 53 ORDER BY Work_Type DESC;
SELECT T2.Work_Type, T1.Name FROM editor AS T1 JOIN journal_committee AS T2 ON T1.Editor_ID = T2.Editor_ID ORDER BY T2.Work_Type DESC;
SELECT Sales, journal.Journal_ID FROM journal JOIN journal_committee ON journal_committee.Journal_ID = journal.Journal_ID WHERE journal_committee.Journal_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Sales = 76

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T1.Date), T1.Theme FROM journal AS T1 WHERE T1.Sales < 73 AND T1.Sales IN (SELECT T1.Sales FROM journal AS T1 WHERE T1.Sales BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND T1.Journal_ID >= 3) GROUP BY T1.Theme HAVING SUM(T1.Journal_ID) < 59
SELECT Age, Name FROM editor LIMIT 3
SELECT Editor_ID FROM editor WHERE Editor_ID IN (SELECT Editor_ID FROM journal_committee);
SELECT MIN(Journal_ID), COUNT(DISTINCT Sales), MIN(Date) AS Date FROM journal GROUP BY MIN(Date) HAVING SUM(Journal_ID) = 49 ORDER BY MIN(Date) DESC
SELECT Work_Type FROM journal_committee WHERE  Journal_ID = 38
SELECT MAX(T1.Journal_ID), SUM(T3.Age), T1.Date FROM journal AS T1 JOIN journal_committee AS T2 ON T1.Journal_ID = T2.Journal_ID JOIN editor AS T3 ON T2.Editor_ID = T3.Editor_ID ORDER BY T1.Date DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T1.Theme), COUNT(DISTINCT T3.Name), T1.Date FROM journal AS T1 JOIN journal_committee AS T2 ON T1.Journal_ID = T2.Journal_ID JOIN editor AS T3 ON T3.Editor_ID = T2.Editor_ID WHERE T1.Journal_ID > 40 GROUP BY T1.Date ORDER BY T1.Date DESC LIMIT 7;

SELECT T1.Date, T1.Theme FROM journal AS T1 INNER JOIN journal_committee AS T2 ON T1.Journal_ID = T2.Journal_ID INNER JOIN editor AS T3 ON T2.Editor_ID = T3.Editor_ID WHERE T2.Journal_ID >= 25 AND T2.Journal_ID IN (SELECT Journal_ID FROM journal_committee WHERE Journal_ID != 0) ORDER BY T1.Date ASC LIMIT 9
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Journal_ID), Sales, Date FROM journal WHERE Journal_ID <= 60 GROUP BY Date ORDER BY Date ASC;

SELECT MIN(T1.Journal_ID), MIN(T3.Age), T1.Date FROM journal AS T1 JOIN journal_committee AS T2 ON T1.Journal_ID = T2.Journal_ID JOIN editor AS T3 ON T2.Editor_ID = T3.Editor_ID GROUP BY T1.Date HAVING MAX(T3.Editor_ID) <= 94 ORDER BY T1.Date ASC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT u.Editor_ID), u.Journal_ID FROM journal_committee AS u WHERE  u.Journal_ID = 95
SELECT Editor_ID, Work_Type FROM journal_committee ORDER BY Editor_ID ASC;

SELECT T2.Journal_ID FROM editor AS T1 JOIN journal_committee AS T2 ON T1.Editor_ID = T2.Editor_ID JOIN journal AS T3 ON T2.Journal_ID = T3.Journal_ID WHERE T1.Editor_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND T3.Journal_ID > 0
SELECT Sales, Journal_ID FROM journal
